<h2 id="research" class="govuk-heading-l">Research</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">The pattern is used in the VAT repayments service and was tested with 7 users across 3 rounds.</p>
<p class="govuk-body">Research has shown that users:</p>

<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet" role="list">
  <li> understood that events were connected to one another on a timeline, with one event following another </li>
  <li> easily identified that the top event was the most recent;</li>
  <li>on smaller screens had a similar experience to those on larger devices</li>
</ul>

